Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,One day, at the far reaches of space,\Nthe minor planet Kumaria exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The fragments of Kumaria became a\Nmeteor swarm that rained down on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Which made the world's bears rise up as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:01:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,They all started attacking humans!\NLike, who could've seen that coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The humans built the Wall of Severance\Nto try to drive us bears from their world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,but guess what, man-made rules\Ndon't work on bears! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We are bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:23.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears eat people. It's what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.06,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become true\Nfriends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are... eating someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are the transfer students...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:58.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I get it--they're bears pretending to be human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"I WILL NEVER FORGIVE YOU"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears' cruel attack has ended\NSumika Izumino's earthly life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.77,MainTop,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the student body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:58.91,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko Yurizono will now deliver\Na eulogy for our departed friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino was a gentle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,She showed kindness to the weak,\Nand was always generous with her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,She never lost sight of herself, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.59,MainTop,,0,0,0,,and bore the pure heart her name suggested--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yurizono?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:30.73,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Izumino was like a white wildflower\Nin the fields of spring:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,brave and sweet, yet graceful--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kureha Tsubaki・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe Sumika was eaten by a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not true! It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Forgive Kureha for not being able\Nto come to the memorial today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She's lost someone important to her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You really love her, don't you, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm sure you'll see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,If you wish really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:06:00.57,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I wish,\NI'll never see Sumika again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't protect my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Does the Wall of Severance even\N{\i1}do {\i0}anything? A bear got through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, they say\Nanother girl from that class is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Did the bear get her too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it's off the record since\Nthey haven't found a body yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:30.97,Main,,0,0,0,,--Bears are seriously vermin.\N--Growl. Those girls look so tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:36.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl Kureha Tsubaki wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right. We can't target her\Nif she doesn't come to school, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:45.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki has a delicious smell, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee, you have a gorgeous wild-animal\Nsmell when you're being cool, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oooh, your smell makes me giddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I just had a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.\NGinko Yurishiro and Lulu Yurigasaki--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,those transfer students are bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:22.90,Main,,0,0,0,,This is horrible. But what I saw\Nat the flowerbed is hard evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuko. Mitsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Konomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:35.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Your head's in the clouds. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're acting weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really so concerned about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki. I know\Nyou're trying to get close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,But why? If you make friends with her,\Nthe Invisible Storm will attack you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll cause you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that Sumika Izumino is dead,\Nshe's obviously going to be next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Kureha Tsubaki didn't back\Ndown on her love of Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls who don't follow the mood\Nof the herd get excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how the system works, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.80,Main,,0,0,0,,There's just something that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it? If you're worried\Nabout something, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,All right. The truth is, I saw something awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello! It's the transfer students,\NLulu Yurigasaki and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.36,MainTop,,0,0,0,,...Ginko Yurishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we want you to let us have a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! What a cute house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not using the attic, right?\NCan we live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking ab--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Wah! Ginko and I have been sleeping\Noutside ever since we moved to town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I itch all over! Any longer and I'll get fleas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't we at least use your bath?\NWhat's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, if it's just the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:23.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! Negotiation successful! I'm so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! It's just for today, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... ah, Yurigasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You can call me Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And you can call me Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I taste tears, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:51.59,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Bathing, bathing, baths are so fun! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:56.30,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Bubbles, bubbles everywhere,\Ngrowl, growl, growl! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't have a room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but after you drink that,\Ntake Yurigasaki and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you crying, growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I wasn't crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Did you know that sad\Nand lonely tears taste like a treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... This is heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Muahaha, we've safely invaded Kureha's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}so {\i0}clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, will you two go away\Nonce Yurigasaki is done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll let you take a bath too, if you need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with this girl? She keeps staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to mention she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,And she talks funny,\Nwith all that "growl" stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, your love is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The taste of tears... Your love is true, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What would {\i1}you {\i0}know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. Because my love is true, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't know! You don't know\Na thing about me and Sumika,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,so don't talk like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:14.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki. I've longed to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,We came here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You smell, a delicious smell! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll show you my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Get away from Kureha right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, Lulu Yurigasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I know what you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw. I saw what you were doing that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Now get away! I won't let you\Nlay a finger on Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Show your true colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ngggh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn, that was a quick retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono, what--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:55.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a challenge from the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki,\Nif your love is true, go to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Give yourself over to the bears,\Nand your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What does that mean? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,My love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko loves that girl Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko belongs to {\i1}me{\i0}!\NI won't let anyone else have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That Kureha Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I, Konomi Yurikawa, will eat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The time for judgment has come, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive those bears.\NI'll {\i1}ruin {\i0}those bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What flowers will you plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuri{\i0}--lilies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Lilies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,They're my mother's flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're really growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought lily bulbs were just\Nsomething to put in egg custards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Silly Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope they bloom soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Not long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Your love will bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,My love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,My love...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll prove my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive bears. I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Nas-ss-ss-ss-sty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I keep missing. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Die, beast! Die, die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It killed Sumika. I... I have to kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to eat her! I want to eat her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Court is in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.66,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Severance Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:18:00.25,MainTop,,0,0,0,,We now begin the Yuri Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, less than a week has passed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,since the defendant-bears\Nlast preyed on a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:16.51,MainTop,,0,0,0,,This is blatant overeating. They are guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:22.06,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Objection! I think what constitutes\N"mega-hungry" is different for every bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears follow bear instincts--that is the sexy way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant-bears, I ask you:\NWill you be invisible? Or will you eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I now declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:19:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Ra-Ra-Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I'm going to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is what I hope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm searching in the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Searching for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Searching for it where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:50.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me the Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That was close.\NAre you okay, Kureha? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,There are two bears. There must\Nbe one more lurking somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:32.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Bears are cautious.\NThey won't attack again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, you mustn't blame yourself.\NIzumino's death isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She was just a little unluckier\Nthan the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,No... that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand. I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay to cry, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You were Izumino's true friend.\NYou have the right to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Unit 105.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We found a dead bear on the Arashigaoka\NHigh School access road. I repeat--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sweet Kureha, your love belongs to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're so good I {\i1}ache{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But not tonight, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, grawr. Chomp, chomp, grawr.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no good. Invisible girls\Nwill only ever taste invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,After tearing apart so many of them,\NI finally understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Only excluded individuals are truly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only the meat of girls\Nwho won't back down on love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,that tastes like pomegranates\Nand honey--that satisfies my hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino, you tasted wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:53.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon... the Invisible Storm will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:23:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to eat you this minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...Tsubaki Kureha! Grawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
